transcript:
Customer: The person you have called is speaking to someone else. You can wait or call again later. Aapne jis
Executive: Hello. Hello. Hanji sir, namaskar Aditya baat kar raha hu.
Customer: Ji toh boliye.
Executive: Aapne 3 baje 3 baje ka time diya tha na sir?
Customer: Sir abhi toh lunch karne ja rahe the. Toh thoda lunch kar le uske baad hum log baithenge.
Executive: Ek minute lagega sir, bas ek minute aapke baat karna tha. Keh rahe the toh dekhiye aapka jo hai jo hamara ye tha na ispe ki call tha. Toh main ye bas puchna chah raha tha ki wo jo raise hua tha sir ki matlab aapne isi ke andar raise kiya tha ki aapko buyleads nahi dikh rahi hai aur wo cheeze nahi dikh rahi thi. Toh uske regarding toh main aapse concern kar raha hu aur ek cheez aur sir ki jo aap aage se koi bhi call kiya kariye na sir toh wo mere number pe kiya kariye. Toh uske related ek concern raise tha usko main close kar du sir?
Customer: Kya ji bole?
Executive: Keh rahe hai concern raise tha na ki aapne mujhe direct nahi call karke aapne direct 9696 pe call kar diya tha. Toh wo concern raise tha toh use band kar de raha hu na kyuki aap toh mujhse contact kar hi sakte hai.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai, usko main close kar de raha hu. Mainly uski baat thi ki wo close wo close kar du aur sath mein sir suniye main keh raha tha ki aapne na maine fir abhi bhi ye 3D jo sign board hai aapka 3D outdoor sign board jo hai us usme maine uski mapping maine theek ki hai. Theek hai aur ek do product hai sir jo maine aapke jo competitor hai na unme se ek the wo cheeze jo unke mein better lag rahi thi aur aapme thoda sa thoda sa lag rahi thoda sa ajeeb lag raha tha use maine change kiya hai. Theek hai toh aapko fir uske baad aaiyega toh kuch cheeze mujhe dikhani hai jo dekh ke hum usko clear karte hai. Theek hai aur buyleads ko related bhi baat kar lete hai. Accha sir ek cheez aur us waqt jo buylead maine aapko bataya tha wo consume kiya aapne?
Customer: Ji abhi toh just free hua hu.
Executive: Are yaar 12 minute hua tha sir us waqt agar consume kiye hote toh kuch toh waha se result milta milta. Chaliye theek hai koi baat nahi abhi free hue hai aap khana wana kha lijiye fir hum aaram se uske regarding milke baat karte hai. Baki main wo concern close kare raha hu okay?
Customer: Theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer raised issue of not seeing buyleads.

- Customer called on a different number.



Resolution:

- Executive is working on customer's 3D sign board.

- Executive is closing the concern raised.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will call back after lunch.



Alert (If Any):

None
